  "content": " <div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"9420\" class=\"elementor elementor-9420\" data-elementor-settings=\"{&quot;ha_cmc_init_switcher&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\"> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-7a7f031 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"7a7f031\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-52f45e0\" data-id=\"52f45e0\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4979518 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"4979518\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\" data-ad-layout=\"in-article\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"6261327459\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-1001c23 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"1001c23\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f4831cb\" data-id=\"f4831cb\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-79e78ea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"79e78ea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Genital Ulcer Syndrome</span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Genital ulcer disease is a common syndrome affecting both men and women, characterized by </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">single or multiple ulcers</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> with different clinical manifestations. </span></p><blockquote style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Genital ulcer disease</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> refers to </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">breaks in the skin or mucosa and may present as ulcers, sores or vesicles</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. </span></blockquote><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 3pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Case Definition:</span></p><p> </p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt; padding: 3pt 0pt 0pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Non-vesicular Genital Ulcer</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Ulcer on the penis, scrotum, or rectum in men, and on the labia, vagina, or rectum in women, with or without inguinal adenopathy. Vesicular ulcers involve the presence or history of vesicles.</span></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c9222d1 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c9222d1\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-179bc1a\" data-id=\"179bc1a\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4e6d2d elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"b4e6d2d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block; text-align:center;\" data-ad-layout=\"in-article\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"6261327459\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-3a8bbb5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3a8bbb5\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6211c16\" data-id=\"6211c16\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8caa51f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8caa51f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Causes</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span></h4><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The aetiology of this syndrome varies across geographical regions and can evolve over time, often presenting challenges due to mixed infections and the influence of HIV.</span></p><ol><li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Non-vesicular Ulcers:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Commonly caused by syphilis, chancroid, lymphogranuloma venereum, granuloma inguinale, or atypical cases of genital herpes (HSV infection).</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Vesicular Ulcers</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Primarily caused by Herpes genitalis, syphilis, and Chancroid in Uganda.</span></li></ol><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Multiple organisms can cause genital sores, commonly:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Treponema pallidum bacteria: syphilis</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Herpes simplex virus: genital herpes</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Haemophilus ducreyi: Chancroid</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Donovania granulomatis: Granuloma inguinale</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Chlamydia strains: lymphogranuloma venereum (LGV)</span></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d63cc39 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d63cc39\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-9e8ab5b\" data-id=\"9e8ab5b\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7996bc9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"7996bc9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>  <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"7570414357\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-85b6515 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"85b6515\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-f649144\" data-id=\"f649144\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5551ee6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5551ee6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 3pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Clinical Presentation:</span></h4><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 3pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In men, genital ulcer disease occurring under the prepuce may present with a discharge in uncircumcised male patients, therefore, prepuce should be retracted and examined for ulcer lesions. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Female patients should have the labia separated and inspected, with speculum examination if necessary.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Mixed infections are common</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Primary syphilis</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: the ulcer is at first painless and may be between or on the labia or on the penis.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Secondary syphilis</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: multiple, painless ulcers on the penis or vulva.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Genital Herpes</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: small, multiple, usually painful blisters, vesicles, or ulcers. Often recurrent.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Granuloma inguinale</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: an irregular ulcer which increases in size and may cover a large area.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Chancroid</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: multiple, large, irregular ulcers with enlarged painful suppurating lymph nodes.</span></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-0fdb859 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"0fdb859\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8e72762\" data-id=\"8e72762\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b47ec79 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"b47ec79\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-layout-key=\"-6q+ef+1v-2m-h\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"2010257102\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4f05c51 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4f05c51\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ddab93c\" data-id=\"ddab93c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f6fdd8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5f6fdd8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 3pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Management</span><span style=\"font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">:</span></h4><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 3pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prompt treatment is important due to the increased risk of HIV transmission associated with genital ulcers. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Treatment strategies for both genders should align with the local epidemiology. In Uganda, the following approach is recommended:</span></p><ol><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Non-vesicular Ulcers</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Treatment according to the provided </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">flow chart</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, distinguishing between specific etiologies.</span></li><li><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-60c719b1-7fff-93bb-585c-53bcffccae36\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Vesicular Ulcers:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #374151; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> Given the increased risk of HIV transmission, treatment for </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #374151; background-color: #d9ead3; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">genital herpes</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #374151; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> is strongly recommended.</span></span></li></ol><p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-9423 size-full\" src=\"/images/Genital-Ulcer-Disease-Flow-Chart.png\" alt=\"Genital Ulcer Disease Flow Chart\" width=\"728\" height=\"795\" srcset=\"/images/Genital-Ulcer-Disease-Flow-Chart.png 728w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Genital-Ulcer-Disease-Flow-Chart-600x655.png 600w, https://nursesrevisionuganda.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Genital-Ulcer-Disease-Flow-Chart-275x300.png 275w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\" /></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: underline; -webkit-text-decoration-skip: none; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Management Protocol for Genital Ulcer Syndrome:</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Multiple Painful Blisters or Vesicles (Likely Herpes):</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Administer Aciclovir 400 mg every 6 hours for 7 days.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If RPR (Rapid Plasma Reagin) positive, add Benzathine penicillin 2.4 MU IM single dose (half in each buttock).</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In case of persistent lesions, repeat Acyclovir for an additional 7 days.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">All Other Cases:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Prescribe Ciprofloxacin 500 mg every 12 hours for 3 days.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Add Benzathine penicillin 2.4 MU IM single dose (half in each buttock).</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">For individuals with penicillin allergy, substitute with Erythromycin 500 mg every 6 hours for 14 days.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If Ulcer Persists Beyond 10 Days and Partner Was Treated:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Add Erythromycin 500 mg every 6 hours for 7 days.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">If Ulcer Still Persists:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Refer the individual for specialist management.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15pt; margin-bottom: 15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Important Notes:</span></p><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A negative RPR does not exclude early syphilis.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Genital ulcers may appear with enlarged and</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #0d0d0d; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">fluctuating inguinal lymph nodes (buboes). Do not incise buboes.</span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 3pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Other Components of STI Case Management:</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 3pt 0pt 15pt 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">In addition to antimicrobial therapy, comprehensive STI case management includes:</span></p><ol><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Partner Notification and Treatment:</span> <span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Partners should be notified and treated, irrespective of symptoms.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Preventive Measures:</span> <span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Emphasize preventive measures, including safe sexual practices and condom use.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #fff2cc; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Health Education</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Counsel and educate all clients on:</span></li></ol><ul><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">The importance of treatment compliance and regular follow-ups.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Condom use and provide condoms.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Partner management.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Offer or refer for HIV VCT services if necessary.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Schedule a return visit if feasible.</span></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Poppins,sans-serif; color: #374151; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Abstaining from sex symptoms resolve.</span></li></ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ad8be9e elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"ad8be9e\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a5e9d88\" data-id=\"a5e9d88\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c95befa elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"c95befa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"1271890507\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-f74004b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"f74004b\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-d3f1c68\" data-id=\"d3f1c68\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3ff1194 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3ff1194\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <h2><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-eacf22ed-7fff-33c8-8661-92c092bae795\"><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; color: #374151; background-color: #ead1dc; font-weight: bold; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Inguinal Buboes Syndrome</span></span></h2><p></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-b8ff7fc elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"b8ff7fc\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ha_eqh_enable&quot;:false}\"> <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\"> <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-98d1cde\" data-id=\"98d1cde\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\"> <div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7a9faa5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"7a9faa5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\"> <div class=\"elementor-widget-container\"> <script async src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5767364969818632\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:block\" data-ad-format=\"fluid\" data-ad-layout-key=\"-6q+ef+1v-2m-h\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5767364969818632\" data-ad-slot=\"2010257102\"></ins>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </div> <!-- .entry-content .clear --> ",
  "semester": "year-1-semester-1"
}